description: The French military deployment comes amid Greek-Turkish tension over oil and gas exploration.
title: France sends jets and ships to tense east Mediterranean
title_page: France sends jets and ships to tense east Mediterranean - BBC News
maintext: The French frigate La Fayette has been on exercises with the Greek navy and is staying in the area. The Rafale jets were in Cyprus for an exercise and are now relocating to Souda, on the Greek island of Crete.
